{"id": "work_cd4d9976-cbf4-529f-8535-a9e5ece01e70", "title": "Observation of High Coherence in Josephson Junction Qubits Measured in a Three-Dimensional Circuit QED Architecture", "sources": [{"source": "dtic", "id": "pub.1047963202"}], "last_updated": "2026-03-09T19:36:43.629190", "abstract": "Superconducting quantum circuits based on Josephson junctions have made rapid progress in demonstrating quantum behavior and scalability. However, the future prospects ultimately depend upon the intrinsic coherence of Josephson junctions, and whether superconducting qubits can be adequately isolated from their environment. We introduce a new architecture for superconducting quantum circuits employing a three-dimensional resonator that suppresses qubit decoherence while maintaining sufficient coupling to the control signal. With the new architecture, we demonstrate that Josephson junction qubits are highly coherent, with T2 \u223c 10 to 20\u2009\u2009\u03bcs without the use of spin echo, and highly stable, showing no evidence for 1/f critical current noise. These results suggest that the overall quality of Josephson junctions in these qubits will allow error rates of a few 10(-4), approaching the error correction threshold.", "publication_date": "2011-12-05", "doi": "10.1103/physrevlett.107.240501", "url": "https://dtic.dimensions.ai/details/publication/pub.1047963202?and_facet_researcher=ur.015527265674.84", "citation_count": 0, "authors": [{"author_id": "author_a8e8a052-5104-520d-b353-69d002d6b476", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_78542dd0-c538-5434-8d2c-fe6f77c8cde3", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_c758827b-3356-5691-aab4-b8395042bbf8", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_6e7db33e-e505-5c7a-8c36-a20775d68ae6", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_dbe9cf4b-b492-5b37-81e7-2b16bd2e3b3c", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_5b878ed3-da16-59af-9468-632b6538e369", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_161bc9f4-7392-5c2b-9b2f-a41ce9b126d2", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_9d5879d4-8089-5f56-b670-eb3552fa6891", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_d2b8b900-5488-5f87-ab9d-06fb3b0ff50b", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_54fe32c4-bd8d-5b83-86ab-69d80ac3306c", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_05d4b046-8319-56cd-a216-425dff836a4f", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_f3887ae3-1997-5c7c-bacd-477f516abf7d", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_b7f874c0-f80b-59b0-ae92-d836f62f2b84", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}], "orgs": [{"org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df", "role": "affiliation"}, {"org_id": "org_4c22fa8e-32a3-59f9-b028-77da8576d83c", "role": "affiliation"}, {"org_id": "org_9dac9558-93cb-59a1-8f5c-15af8f7be910", "role": "affiliation"}, {"org_id": "org_994caab0-2043-5c82-8ff9-bd7f0709eb4e", "role": "affiliation"}], "topics": [{"topic_id": "topic_40c92d30-1e13-51c2-a6bc-692493c876ff", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_7ced97ac-1108-5195-b3a2-d664e9eb9af5", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_221a5cf0-5e73-5e2b-ba8e-2c0b66d37feb", "score": 1.0}], "created_at": "2026-03-09T19:36:43.629190"}